Learn About the Digital Insurance Platform
See Insurance in Action with the Insurance Application Suite

Harmonized Insurance Policy Object Model

It's time! You can use the Insurance Policy core object model on Salesforce FSC for all your insurance policy data.

Broker Digital Experience Site
Your brokers and agents need access to quotes, policies, and accounts they work with to sell insurance products and manage existing policies.

Policyholder Digital Experience Site
Your policyholders need access to view and make changes to their account, policies, claims, and billing information.

Group Voluntary Benefits Application
Your users can cut down the time they spend on finding the ideal plan and then enrolling employees.

Property & Casualty Application Spring '21
Your users can now file a FNOL for a multi auto policy using a guided flow.

Odds and Ends in Insurance Spring '21
In addition to the big features described above, we've made a few smaller changes to Vlocity Insurance that we want you to know about.

Relationship Graphs
Refresh Relationship Graphs programmatically, use additional filter operators, and include one-to-many relationships in Timeline graphs.
